detailing how we intend to implement resolutions 425 and 426," he
said.
</P>
<P>
"I have heard the reports of what's happening on the ground;
but obviously, I am waiting for the detailed report from my men to
be able to analyze it. But I do hope that what is happening will
not unduly affect the plans that I shall be putting forward today,
" the U.N. chief added.
</P>
<P>
Israel has informed the United Nations that it will withdraw
all its troops from southern Lebanon by July.
</P>
<P>
The United Nations is planning to increase the personnel of
the United Nations Interim Force in Lebanon after the withdrawal
of Israeli troops. 
