<HEADLINE> Eritrea Repulses Ethiopian Forces on Two Fronts </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NAIROBI, May 22 (Xinhua) -- Eritrea claimed on Monday that its
troops had repulsed the Ethiopian forces on two fronts, killing
and wounding hundreds of Ethiopian soldiers, said a Eritrean press
release available here.
</P>
<P>
The Eritrean Foreign Ministry said in the release that the
Ethiopian army launched the attacks on Eritrean positions Sunday.
</P>
<P>
