for a long period of time and the two countries have supported
each other on many issues in international affairs.
</P>
<P>
He said that on the principles of equality and mutual benefit,
the two countries would further develop cooperation in many areas
including economy, culture and information.
</P>
<P>
Xinhua News Agency is ready to broaden the cooperation with the
Kenya News Agency and other local media and to offer better
service to them, Zhang added.
</P>
<P>
Present on the occasion were Chinese Ambassador to Kenya An
Yongyu and other Kenyan officials. 
