<TEXT>
<P>
YANTAI, May 22 (Xinhua) -- Prioritizing technological
innovations and their application have boosted the development of
the local marine economy in Yantai, a coastal city in east China's
Shandong Province.
</P>
<P>
Yantai has take the initiative to establish an all-level
service network aimed at promoting the use of new marine
technology. The city has already set up offices in all its 57
counties and townships, employing more than 2,000 scientific
researchers to promote and develop new marine technology.
</P>
