<HEADLINE> Xinhua Article on Jiang's Important Remarks on Role of Communist Party </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, May 22 (Xinhua) -- Xinhua News Agency published today
a special commentator's article on Jiang Zemin's recent remarks on
the role of the Communist Party of China (CPC).
</P>
<P>
Jiang, the state president and general secretary of the CPC,
said during a recent tour to south and east China that the Party
must always meet the requirements for the development of China's
advanced productivity, lead the orientation of the development of
advanced culture, and represent the fundamental interests of the
Chinese people.
</P>
<P>
This is a principle the Party must follow for further
development, says the article, entitled The Root for Building the
Party, the Base for Ruling, and the Source of Power.
</P>
<P>
The Party prospers, wins the support of the people, and can
overcome any difficulty when adhering to this principle.
</P>
<P>
If the Party adheres to this principle, it will never be
defeated, it will be cordially supported by the Chinese people of
different ethnic groups, and will lead the people from victory to
victory, says the article.
</P>
<P>
Ever since the Party was founded, it has been an advanced
political party marching ahead of China's social development, and
according to the Party Constitution, the CPC is the pioneer of the
Chinese working class, the article says.
</P>
<P>
It says that Jiang's remarks are an answer to building the
Party, provide a new impetus for the nature, motto and fundamental
tasks of the Party, a new development of the Marxist theory on
Party building, a new demand for Party organizations at all levels
and all Party members and cadres.
</P>
<P>
It urges Party members to seriously study and deeply understand
the importance of Jiang's remarks and to strengthen the Party
according to the them.
</P>
<P>
Jiang's remarks will also help strengthen and improve the Party
in the new century, the article says. 
</P>
</TEXT>
