<HEADLINE> Int'l Turf, Landscape and Equipment Expo to be Held in Beijing </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, May 22 (Xinhua) -- China International Turf, Landscape
and Equipment Expo 2000 will be held at the Beijing National
Agriculture Exhibition Center from September 26 to 29 this year.
</P>
<P>
The expo, the second of its kind in China, will feature quality
turf, seeds, advanced equipment, and the latest landscape
technology. More than 100 domestic and overseas enterprises are
expected to participate in the expo, which will cover an area of
over 8,000 square meters.
</P>
<P>
An expo organizer said that preferential treatment will be
given to participant enterprises from China's western regions,
where a large campaign to plant trees and vegetation in arid areas
is under way.
</P>
<P>
The expo is sponsored by the China Forestry Machinery
Association, the China Seed Group and the Beijing Zhongnong
Exhibition Center under the auspices of the China National
Greening Committee. 
</P>
