<TEXT>
<P>
WELLINGTON, May 22 (Xinhua) -- New Zealand Prime Minister Helen
Clark issued a statement here Monday, saying her government
strongly believes that it is within the Fijian constitution that
the current political crisis there must be resolved.
</P>
