-- The State Forestry Administration has crafted a plan that it
hopes will limit desertification, which is one of China's most
serious problems.
</P>
<P>
-- Tung Chee-hwa, Hong Kong chief executive, Saturday called on
Taiwan's new leader, Chen Shui-bian, to unequivocally accept the
principle of one China in which Taiwan is a part of China.
</P>
